        public T withAmount(MonetaryAmount amount)

      • withSuspenseItem

        public T withSuspenseItem(java.lang.String policyNumber,
                 MonetaryAmount netAmount)
        Adds a suspense item to the distribution, with the given policy number, and net amount to apply. Also increments the amount of the money by the proper net amount for this suspense item. We cannot guess the producer from a suspense item. So producer will need to be specified. We will assume 10% commission rate to calculate the gross and commission from the given net amount
        Parameters:
        policyNumber - The policy number string to identify what this suspense item is supposed to be held for
        netAmount - The net amount to apply on the suspense item
        Returns:
        This builder

      • withFullDistributionFor

        public T withFullDistributionFor(PolicyPeriod policyPeriod)
        Fully distributes all the invoice items on the policy period (grossAmountToApply = grossAmountUnsettled and commissionAmountToApply = PrimaryCommissionReserve).

        Unless another producer payer is specified, will also initialize the producer payer to be the producer of the primary policy commission of the policy period.

        Parameters:
        policyPeriod - The policy period to fully pay/promise
        Returns:
        This builder

      • withFullDistributionFor

        public T withFullDistributionFor(Invoice invoice)
        Fully distributes all the invoice items on the invoice (grossAmountToApply = grossAmountUnsettled and commissionAmountToApply = PrimaryCommissionReserve).

        Unless another producer payer is specified, if this invoice is a statement invoice, will also initialize the producer payer to be the producer who is paying the statement invoice

        Parameters:
        invoice - The invoice to fully pay/promise
        Returns:
        This builder

      • withFullDistributionFor

        public T withFullDistributionFor(InvoiceItem... invoiceItems)
        Fully distributes all the invoice items (grossAmountToApply = grossAmountUnsettled and commissionAmountToApply = PrimaryCommissionReserve).

        Unless another producer payer is specified, and if all of the provided invoice items are currently earning on the same producer in the primary active role, will also initialize the producer payer to that producer.

        Parameters:
        invoiceItems - The invoice items to fully pay/promise
        Returns:
        this builder
